The key trends for the Mercedes-Benz Group are (as at the financial year ending 31 December):

===Management===
Ola Källenius became the Chairman of Mercedes-Benz Group and Head of Mercedes-Benz Cars on 22 May 2019. , the members of the Board of Management of Mercedes-Benz Group AG were:
