===Chapels===
*Loreto&#x27;s Chapel
*Virgen de Guadalupe

===Transportation===
The city is served by Alcantarí Airport with multiple domestic destinations on three commercial airlines.

==Twin towns – sister cities==
* La Plata, Argentina
* San Miguel de Tucumán, Argentina
* Ushuaia, Argentina
* Concepción, Chile

